Quiz 40 Light Component Type

1. Rotating this light will not change the lighting of the scene

- Point

2. Which type of light is this

- Area

3. Which type of light is this?

- Spot

4. Which type of light is this

- Point

5. Which type of ligh is this

- Directional

6. What is meant by a Culling Mask as it relates to lighting?

- A selection of layers preventing GameObjects from being illuminated by one light

7. What effect is being used here?

- Cookie

8. What effect is this?

- Halo

9. Name the following effect

- Lens flare